            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿لَاۤ﴾ زائدة في الموضعين ﴿أُقۡسِمُ بِیَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِیَـٰمَةِ ۝١﴾</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "75:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَلَاۤ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلنَّفۡسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ ۝٢﴾ الَّتِي تَلُوم نَفْسهَا وَإِنْ اجْتَهَدَتْ فِي الْإِحْسَان وَجَوَاب الْقَسَم مَحْذُوف أَيْ لَتُبْعَثُنَّ دَلَّ عليه</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "75:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿أَیَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَـٰنُ﴾ أَيْ الْكَافِر ﴿أَلَّن نَّجۡمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ ۝٣﴾ للبعث والإحياء</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "75:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿بَلَىٰ﴾ نَجْمَعهَا ﴿قَـٰدِرِینَ﴾ مَعَ جَمْعهَا ﴿عَلَىٰۤ أَن نُّسَوِّیَ بَنَانَهُۥ ۝٤﴾ وَهُوَ الْأَصَابِع أَيْ نُعِيد عِظَامهَا كَمَا كَانَتْ مَعَ صِغَرهَا فَكَيْفَ بِالْكَبِيرَةِ</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "75:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿بَلۡ یُرِیدُ ٱلۡإِنسَـٰنُ لِیَفۡجُرَ﴾ اللَّام زَائِدَة وَنَصَبَهُ بِأَنْ مُقَدَّرَة أَيْ أَنْ يُكَذِّب ﴿أَمَامَهُۥ ۝٥﴾ أَيْ يَوْم الْقِيَامَة دَلَّ عَلَيْهِ</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "75:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿یَسۡـَٔلُ أَیَّانَ﴾ مَتَى ﴿یَوۡمُ ٱلۡقِیَـٰمَةِ ۝٦﴾ سُؤَال اسْتِهْزَاء وتكذيب</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "75:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ ۝٧﴾ بكسر الراء وفتحها دَهَشَ وَتَحَيَّرَ لِمَا رَأَى مِمَّا كَانَ يُكَذِّبهُ</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "75:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَخَسَفَ ٱلۡقَمَرُ ۝٨﴾ أظلم وذهب ضوؤه</h2>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "75:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ ۝٩﴾ فَطَلَعَا مِنْ الْمَغْرِب أَوْ ذهب ضوؤهما وَذَلِكَ فِي يَوْم الْقِيَامَة</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "75:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿یَقُولُ ٱلۡإِنسَـٰنُ یَوۡمَىِٕذٍ أَیۡنَ ٱلۡمَفَرُّ ۝١٠﴾ الْفِرَار</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "75:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿كَلَّا﴾ رَدْع عَنْ طَلَب الْفِرَار ﴿لَا وَزَرَ ۝١١﴾ لَا مَلْجَأ يَتَحَصَّن بِهِ</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "75:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ یَوۡمَىِٕذٍ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقَرُّ ۝١٢﴾ مُسْتَقَرّ الْخَلَائِق فَيُحَاسَبُونَ ويجازون</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "75:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿یُنَبَّؤُا۟ ٱلۡإِنسَـٰنُ یَوۡمَىِٕذِۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ ۝١٣﴾ بِأَوَّلِ عمله وآخره</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "75:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿بَلِ ٱلۡإِنسَـٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفۡسِهِۦ بَصِیرَةࣱ ۝١٤﴾ شاهد تنطلق جَوَارِحه بِعَمَلِهِ وَالْهَاء لِلْمُبَالَغَةِ فَلَا بُدّ مِنْ جزائه</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "75:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَلَوۡ أَلۡقَىٰ مَعَاذِیرَهُۥ ۝١٥﴾ جَمْع مَعْذِرَة عَلَى غَيْر قِيَاس أَيْ لَوْ جَاءَ بِكُلِّ مَعْذِرَة مَا قبلت منه</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "75:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>تَعَالَى لِنَبِيِّهِ ﴿لَا تُحَرِّكۡ بِهِۦ﴾ بِالْقُرْآنِ قَبْل فَرَاغ جِبْرِيل مِنْهُ ﴿لِسَانَكَ لِتَعۡجَلَ بِهِۦۤ ۝١٦﴾ خَوْف أَنْ يَنْفَلِت مِنْك</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "75:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿إِنَّ عَلَیۡنَا جَمۡعَهُۥ﴾ فِي صَدْرك ﴿وَقُرۡءَانَهُۥ ۝١٧﴾ قِرَاءَتك إيَّاهُ أَيْ جَرَيَانه عَلَى لِسَانك</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "75:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَإِذَا قَرَأۡنَـٰهُ﴾ عَلَيْك بِقِرَاءَةِ جِبْرِيل ﴿فَٱتَّبِعۡ قُرۡءَانَهُۥ ۝١٨﴾ اسْتَمِعْ قِرَاءَته فَكَانَ صَلَّى اللَّه عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ يَسْتَمِع ثُمَّ يَقْرَؤُهُ</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "75:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَیۡنَا بَیَانَهُۥ ۝١٩﴾ بِالتَّفْهِيمِ لَك وَالْمُنَاسَبَة بَيْن هَذِهِ الْآيَة وَمَا قَبْلهَا أَنَّ تِلْكَ تَضَمَّنَتْ الْإِعْرَاض عَنْ آيَات اللَّه وَهَذِهِ تَضَمَّنَتْ الْمُبَادَرَة إلَيْهَا بِحِفْظِهَا</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "75:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿كَلَّا﴾ اسْتِفْتَاح بِمَعْنَى أَلَا ﴿بَلۡ یُحِبُّونَ ٱلۡعَاجِلَةَ ۝٢٠﴾ الدُّنْيَا بِالْيَاءِ وَالتَّاء فِي الْفِعْلَيْنِ</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "75:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَیَذَرُونَ ٱلۡـَٔاخِرَةَ ۝٢١﴾ فَلَا يَعْمَلُونَ لَهَا</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "75:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وُجُوهࣱ یَوۡمَىِٕذࣲ﴾ أَيْ فِي يَوْم الْقِيَامَة ﴿نَّاضِرَةٌ ۝٢٢﴾ حسنة مضيئة</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "75:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةࣱ ۝٢٣﴾ أَيْ يَرَوْنَ اللَّه سُبْحَانه وَتَعَالَى فِي الْآخِرَة</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "75:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَوُجُوهࣱ یَوۡمَىِٕذِۭ بَاسِرَةࣱ ۝٢٤﴾ كَالِحَة شَدِيدَة الْعُبُوس</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "75:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿تَظُنُّ﴾ تُوقِن ﴿أَن یُفۡعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةࣱ ۝٢٥﴾ دَاهِيَة عَظِيمَة تكسر فقار الظهر</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "75:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿كَلَّاۤ﴾ بمعنى ألا ﴿إِذَا بَلَغَتِ﴾ النَّفْس ﴿ٱلتَّرَاقِیَ ۝٢٦﴾ عِظَام الْحَلْق</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "75:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَقِیلَ﴾ قال من حوله ﴿مَنۡۜ رَاقࣲ ۝٢٧﴾ يرقيه ليشفى</h2>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "75:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَظَنَّ﴾ أَيْقَنَ مَنْ بَلَغَتْ نَفْسه ذَلِكَ ﴿أَنَّهُ ٱلۡفِرَاقُ ۝٢٨﴾ فراق الدنيا</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "75:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَٱلۡتَفَّتِ ٱلسَّاقُ بِٱلسَّاقِ ۝٢٩﴾ أَيْ إحْدَى سَاقَيْهِ بِالْأُخْرَى عِنْد الْمَوْت أَوْ الْتَفَّتْ شِدَّة فِرَاق الدُّنْيَا بِشِدَّةِ إقْبَال الْآخِرَة</p>"
        },
